# 5. Key User Flows

## 5.1 Organizer Flow
1. **Sign Up** → Select "Organizer" role → Create Organization (name, sport, logo)
2. **Create Group** → Set name, age group, skill level, price, location, schedule
3. **Share Invite Code** → Participants/parents join via 6-character code or QR
4. **Manage Sessions** → View upcoming, create one-off sessions, cancel with reason
5. **Take Attendance** → Open session → See member list → Tap present/absent/late/excused
6. **Send Announcements** → Write message → Push notification sent to all members
7. **Manage Contracts** → Create contract template → Assign to members → Track signatures

## 5.2 Participant Flow (Adult)
1. **Sign Up** → Select "Participant" role
2. **Join Group** → Enter invite code or scan QR → See group info → Confirm join
3. **View Dashboard** → See today's schedule, upcoming sessions across all groups
4. **View Schedule** → Calendar view with color-coded groups
5. **Read Announcements** → Get push notifications, read in-app
6. **Sign Contracts** → View contract details → Digital signature → Download PDF

## 5.3 Parent Flow
1. **Sign Up** → Select "Parent" role → Add children (name, DOB, medical notes)
2. **Join Groups for Children** → Enter invite code → Select which child → Confirm
3. **Unified Dashboard** → See all children's schedules in one view
4. **Per-Child View** → Filter by child to see their groups, upcoming sessions
5. **Sign Contracts** → Sign on behalf of child
6. **Receive Notifications** → Cancellations, announcements, attendance reports

