# 6. UI/UX Design System

## 6.1 Design Philosophy
- **Clean & Friendly**: Rounded corners, soft shadows, plenty of whitespace.
- **Color-Coded Groups**: Each group gets an accent color for instant recognition in calendar/lists.
- **Role-Adaptive UI**: Same app, different dashboards per role. No feature overload.
- **Parent-First for Children**: Parents see a child switcher at the top of their dashboard.

## 6.2 Color Palette

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `primary` | `#6C5CE7` | Main brand purple — buttons, active tabs, links |
| `primary-light` | `#A29BFE` | Light purple — backgrounds, badges |
| `secondary` | `#00B894` | Green — success states, confirmations, attendance "present" |
| `warning` | `#FDCB6E` | Yellow — pending states, upcoming reminders |
| `danger` | `#E17055` | Red-orange — cancellations, absences, delete actions |
| `background` | `#F8F9FD` | App background (light grayish blue) |
| `surface` | `#FFFFFF` | Cards, sheets, modals |
| `text-primary` | `#2D3436` | Main text |
| `text-secondary` | `#636E72` | Secondary/muted text |
| `border` | `#E2E8F0` | Dividers, input borders |

## 6.3 Typography

| Style | Size | Weight | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| `heading-xl` | 28px | Bold (700) | Screen titles |
| `heading-lg` | 22px | SemiBold (600) | Section titles |
| `heading-md` | 18px | SemiBold (600) | Card titles |
| `body` | 16px | Regular (400) | Body text |
| `body-sm` | 14px | Regular (400) | Secondary text, captions |
| `caption` | 12px | Medium (500) | Labels, timestamps |

## 6.4 Spacing & Sizing
- **Border Radius**: Cards `16px`, Buttons `12px`, Inputs `10px`, Avatars `full (9999px)`.
- **Card Shadow**: `shadowColor: "#6C5CE7", shadowOffset: {width: 0, height: 4}, shadowOpacity: 0.08, shadowRadius: 12, elevation: 4`.
- **Padding**: Screen padding `20px`, Card padding `16px`, Section gap `24px`.

## 6.5 Component Patterns
- **Cards**: White surface, 16px radius, subtle shadow, 16px internal padding.
- **Buttons**: Primary (solid purple), Secondary (outlined), Destructive (red-orange). Height: 52px. Full-width on forms.
- **Inputs**: 52px height, 10px radius, 1px border, 16px horizontal padding. Floating label pattern.
- **Avatars**: 48px for lists, 80px for profile headers. Circular. Fallback: colored circle with initials.
- **Bottom Sheets**: Used for quick actions (attendance marking, filters). Snap points: 25%, 50%, 90%.
- **Empty States**: Illustrated (simple vector), with a title, description, and CTA button.
- **Pull-to-Refresh**: On all list screens.

## 6.6 Tab Bar
- 5 tabs: Home, Schedule, Groups, Notifications, Profile
- Icons: `Home`, `Calendar`, `Users`, `Bell`, `User` from lucide
- Active: Primary purple icon + label. Inactive: Gray icon, no label.
- Floating tab bar style with rounded corners and subtle shadow, elevated above content.

